I've created the IScrollBar developer guide at `i-scroll-bar.md`. The document covers:

- **Creating a Scroll Bar**: Using `ScrollBar::New()` and `ScrollBar::DownCast()`
- **Configuring Scroll Bar Visibility**: Setting and getting vertical/horizontal visibility with `ScrollBarVisibility` enum values (`Auto`, `Always`, `Never`)
- **Updating Bar Size and Position**: Using `UpdateBarSize()` and `UpdateScrollPosition()` methods
- **Hiding the Scroll Bar**: Using `HideBar()` for fade-out behavior

All API usage has been verified against the repository headers (`i-scroll-bar.h`, `scroll-bar.h`, `scrollable-enum.h`) and UTC test cases.
